b'The timing of the departure likely spooked a lot of investors given the recent positive headlines in the past month. \n\nI think selling here is a mistake as Marek positions $MYOV better for the Orgovyx rollout in 2021 and also hints that the pipeline is in good shape.'

b"Marek's experience is much more tailored to where $MYOV is heading. \n\nHis work at Amgen with AIMOVIG is particularly notable given the drug was commercialized in a partnership with Novartis (should sound eerily familiar to Myovant's current situation with Pfizer) https://t.co/L5MYt2KIAf"
